<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='933600' id='t-933600'>Chris Anderson:
I really like this metaphor.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='937040' id='t-937040'>How does it link in?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='938600' id='t-938600'>There's a lot of talk in technologyland</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='941760' id='t-941760'>about the personalization of medicine,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='943920' id='t-943920'>that we have all this data
